quotes.quote: Do, or do not. There is no try. - Yoda
I am your father. - Darth Vader
I am a Jedi, like my father before me. - Luke Skywalker

Never tell me the odds! - Han Solo
The Force will be with you, always. - Obi-Wan Kenobi
Raargh! - Chewbacca
This is where the fun begins. - Anakin Skywalker
Your focus determines your reality. - Qui-Gon Jinn
This party's over. - Mace Windu
The dark side of the Force is a pathway to many abilities some consider to be unnatural. - Palpatine
I find your lack of faith disturbing. - Darth Vader
So this is how liberty dies… with thunderous applause. - Padmé Amidala
Fear is the path to the dark side. Fear leads to anger, anger leads to hate, hate leads to suffering. - Yoda
I've got a bad feeling about this. - Various Characters
It's a trap! - Admiral Ackbar
In my experience, there is no such thing as luck. - Obi-Wan Kenobi
I love you. - Leia Organa
I know. - Han Solo
The Force will be with you, Rey. Always. - Luke Skywalker
You were the chosen one! - Obi-Wan Kenobi

You don't know the power of the dark side. - Darth Vader
I am a Jedi, like my father before me. - Luke Skywalker

You will find that it is you who are mistaken, about a great many things. - Obi-Wan Kenobi
